<h2 id="course-organization">Course Organization</h2>

<ul>
  <li>This course is a 50% online course. Most online lectures will be given after midterm.</li>
  <li>All assignments are stepping-stones for the project</li>
  <li>Grading for assignments and the project will be done in terms of functional or operational aspects, not aesthetic points of view</li>
</ul>
